## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of firsthand accounts and the inherent bias in survivor testimonies, which may not fully represent the experiences of all prisoners. Additionally, the focus on specific survival strategies may overlook other significant factors that contributed to survival, such as luck or external aid. The historical context and the passage of time also affect the accuracy and completeness of available data.